{"tid":1278464,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔怪得容量要80GB]《Cyberpunk 2077》有三種不同開局 玩家來譜寫V故事","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:46:55.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8daeb5e3ada5eb32c7c120e63160fac25c2349b","tid":1278464,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2371416906462150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2371416906462150&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3f8e6d4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2371416906462150</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gi4G6V9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgi4G6V9.jpg&h=23b3c245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Multi】《賽博朋克2077》有三種不同開局 玩家來譜寫V故事<br />\n<br />\n  之前我們已經介紹了很多關於《賽博朋克2077》（Cyberpunk 2077）的細節，比如玩家在遊戲中需要做出各種選擇。近日據外媒透露，遊戲一開始玩家需要選擇主角V的童年和背景故事等細節，這些選擇將決定你的開局。<br />\n<br />\n  《賽博朋克2077》首席任務設計師Paweł Sasko表示：&ldquo;在遊戲中玩家可以創建自定義角色，並在三個起源故事之中選擇其一開始遊戲，我們將這系統稱之為&ldquo;lifepaths&rdquo;。玩家可以選擇成為游牧民，Corpo或是流浪漢。每次開局都能有不同的起點和故事背景，這些背景和故事起源有著密切聯繫。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  之前我們介紹過主角V能離開夜城去探索荒地，荒地可能是選擇游牧民開局的玩家起始位置。 Corpo和流浪漢的開局似乎都是在夜城裡開始，但可能在不同的地區。看起來玩家可以完全掌控V的人生軌跡，而不是隨機生成。<br />\n<br />\n  《賽博朋克2077》將於2020年4月16日登陸PS4、Xbox One和PC，遊戲支持中文字幕和配音。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNtpkga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNtpkga.png&h=1bb54936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FbY89v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FbY89v.jpg&h=567d47d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[PS4/Xbox One/PC]《賽博朋克2077》PS4版容量為80GB Xbox One X版支持4K</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1261997/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1261997/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[HEHE]《賽博朋克 2077 (Cyberpunk 2077)》的曖昧對像不會再局限於異性</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1259368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1259368/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3e55e6fd36cf5dc890e1ad084d7fd4e4ca32125c","tid":1278464,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"《電馭叛客2077》（英語：Cyberpunk 2077，中國大陸譯作「賽博朋克2077」，香港常用英文）"},{"pid":"c749ba69d4d82191edc37b299767348a795f40ac","tid":1278464,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202bb879a2999dd4d4620dad374c27e9c6c4d6a5","tid":1278464,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e55e6fd36cf5dc890e1ad084d7fd4e4ca32125c","tid":1278464,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"《電馭叛客2077》（英語：Cyberpunk 2077，中國大陸譯作「賽博朋克2077」，香港常用英文）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"台版譯名好好笑"},{"pid":"f0e1e5f9badf1f402c5f24d91a6af3cdab541a64","tid":1278464,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e55e6fd36cf5dc890e1ad084d7fd4e4ca32125c","tid":1278464,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"《電馭叛客2077》（英語：Cyberpunk 2077，中國大陸譯作「賽博朋克2077」，香港常用英文）"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"用中文唔緊要<br />\n唔好係大陸譯名同簡體字就得"},{"pid":"e05923f29424c764ccff93e4bb456cf9e953c1cf","tid":1278464,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0e1e5f9badf1f402c5f24d91a6af3cdab541a64","tid":1278464,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e55e6fd36cf5dc890e1ad084d7fd4e4ca32125c","tid":1278464,"uid":5320,"li